          "name": "Food Lion (Columbus/Tryon corridor)",
          "approx_drive_min": "10–15",
          "services": "Curbside (select stores), basic grocery",
          "parking": "Plaza lot",
          "notes": "Fast grab for ice, coolers, and paper goods between classes."
